data.title: A Day To Remember f/ Mark Hoppus - “Re-Entry”
data.meta_description: A remix of a song from ADTR’s album released earlier this year goes for Alternative radio adds on January 25, 2022. The remix adds vocals from Mark Hoppus. It has not been released yet.
data.text:

A remix of a song from ADTR’s album released earlier this year goes for Alternative radio adds on January 25, 2022. The remix adds vocals from Mark Hoppus. It has not been released yet.

American Idiot

Diamond Member

Joined: July 2005

Posts: 10,322

Post by American Idiot on

This one was actually in the upper half for me in terms of ranking this very disappointing album. It's not a very good song by any means for ADTR overall material. Decent enough that I was willing to give it another listen, but the "ba ba ba ba" parts are unnecessary filler.

I was so stoked to see some ADTR back on the alternative chart but this sounds so much more like vintage Mark Hoppus than vintage ADTR. And that’s not a terrible thing at all but with all the blink guys having their fingerprints all over everything lately I’d probably prefer that to have been the opposite here.
